name: 'Castle Bam' Print #1 by Rock Publicity
description:
Shot in March 2013 by Leon Hill of Rock Publicity, the 'Castle Bam' print set is a series of five images giving fans an inside look into MTV and 'Jackass' star Bam Margera's house in West Chester, Pennsylvania.

This item is print #1: A shot of one of Bam's cats named Twanda Newton Harris perched on the pool table with the famous metal heartagram on the wall as a backdrop.

Each photo is a high-quality digital print on 18" x 12" canvas mounted on a wooden rectangle frame. Shipping to anywhere in the world.

LIMITED TO 100 PRINTS ONLY!

-- GLOBAL SHIPPING! --

SINGLE ITEM: $30 flat rate globally
ADDITIONAL ITEMS: $15 flat rate globally

OPTION: Order this print hand-numbered and signed by the photographer for an additional $50.00

NOTE: All watermarks/logos will NOT appear on the final print.
